name: Tidewater Midstream and Infrastructure Ltd.
longDescription: Tidewater Midstream and Infrastructure Ltd is a Canadian company that is engaged in providing midstream infrastructure and a natural gas storage facility. It mainly focuses on the purchase, sale, and transportation of Natural Gas Liquids (NGLs) such as propane and natural gasoline throughout North America and export to premium markets. The business activities of the company include gathering, processing, and transportation relates to raw gas gathering systems, processing plants and pipelines, NGL marketing and Extraction, refined products, and other activities. Its business segments consist of Midstream; Downstream; Marketing and extraction and others. The company generates maximum revenue from the Marketing and extraction segment.
